e of Life'?",a:"It's a real-life game where you turn your daily lifestyle content — gym, food, travel, family — into automated income streams using AI. Complete daily tasks across 4 pillars (Health, Wealth, Mindset, Spirit), earn real USD, and level up. Think gamified personal development meets AI automation."},{q:"Do I need coding or tech skills?",a:"Zero. The AI handles 90% of the technical work — content optimization, funnel building, automation. You just follow the daily tasks from your phone. If you can post on Instagram, you can play this game."},{q:"How much time does it take?",a:"30 minutes per day. That's it. The system is designed for busy people with real lives. Complete your daily tasks, check your scorecard, and move on with your day."},{q:"How do I actually earn money?",a:"Through digital product sales, affiliate commissions (50%), and AI-automated income streams. Your lifestyle content gets turned into products that sell 24/7. The Blueprint teaches you the system. Higher levels deploy it for you."},{q:"What kind of content works?",a:"Any lifestyle content. Fitness reels, cooking videos, travel vlogs, daily life stories, family moments. The AI turns whatever you're already doing into monetizable digital products and automated funnels."},{q:"Can I start with Blueprint and upgrade later?",a:"Absolutely. Most players start at Blueprint ($9.90) to learn the game, then upgrade to DFY or Empire when they see results. Your Blueprint investment is credited toward higher levels."},{q:"What if it doesn't work for me?",a:"If you complete the daily tasks for 7 days and don't see value, we'll refund you. No questions asked. We only win when you win."}];function i(){let[e,t]=(0,r.useState)(null);return(0,l.jsx)("section",{id:"faq",className:"section-divider",style:{backgroundColor:"#000000"},children:(0,l.jsxs)("div",{className:"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-20 md:py-28",children:[(0,l.jsx)(a.ay,{children:(0,l.jsxs)("div",{className:"text-center",children:[(0,l.jsx)("di